    <patterns>
      <pattern>Lookup chain: analysisOutputId → sprk_analysisplaybookid → playbook capabilities; follow the existing Dataverse lookup expansion pattern used in other BFF services</pattern>
      <pattern>Redis get-or-set with 30-min TTL: `chat-context:{tenantId}:{sessionId}` — same pattern as DynamicCommandResolver but session-scoped (not record-type-scoped)</pattern>
      <pattern>ChatAnalysisContext assembly: combine results from all 4 query steps into a single immutable record; serialize to JSON for Redis storage</pattern>
      <pattern>Scope query for active scopes: query scopes associated with the analysis or matter via the existing scope association relationship — check existing scope resolution code in PlaybookChatContextProvider</pattern>
    </patterns>
